1. Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/libanezdiaz/SDEV_220_Final_Project_Group_7

2. Navigate into the folder:
cd SDEV_220_Final_Project_Group_7

3. Create virtual environment:
python -m venv venv

4. Activate it:
Windows:
.\venv\Scripts\Activate

5. Install Django:
pip install django

6. Apply migrations:
python manage.py migrate

7. Run the server:
python manage.py runserver

8. Open in browser:
http://127.0.0.1:8000
